  "comment_overrides": {
    "Fact_HR_A": "Supply chain HR cross-functional metrics for workforce planning and performance analysis.\nProvides actuals, budget, and rolling estimate views of key people KPIs including\nFTE headcount, employee turnover (voluntary and involuntary), vacant positions,\npeople cost, and overtime cost \u2014 focused on supply chain functional areas.\nUsed to track workforce efficiency, attrition trends, and labor cost management\nacross company codes, cost centers, and departments.\n\n\nTechnical details:\nSource: hr004_cross_functional_v1 (UNION: main data with RE version mapping + actuals-as-RE for completed periods).\nRE_Version PBI parameter dynamized: MONTH >= 10 \u2192 R100, >= 7 \u2192 R070, >= 4 \u2192 R040, else no RE.\nFiscal period filter: fiscper >= 2 years ago. Version filter: bic_chversion <> R090.\nM transformations: COALESCE nulls (func_area, bic_chrsegmnt \u2192 '000000'), Dept_KEY from SUBSTRING(bic_ca_mcctr, 4, 3)."
  },
